        constructor, this takes in parameters to autmatically set the vaules for the user
        Parameters:
        id - user id, each user has a unique id
        name - name of the user
        email - email of the user, each user must have a unique email
        username - username of the user, each user must have a unique username
        hashed_pass - password that is hashed and stored within the database
        bought_p - number of products the user has bought
        sold_p - number of products the user has sold
        btc_balance - current BitCoin balance the user has
